HEADWORD: Spongin
<hw>Spon"gin</hw> <pr>(sp⟦ucr⟧n"j⟦icr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld> <def>The chemical basis of sponge tissue, a
